{
  "stem": "12051.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow itself, I worked in the sewing room and then the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to report every time anybody came to inspect the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being that I spoke German, I reported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Muller got to know me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I begged him that I wanted to go to Prokocim or to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew my father was in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he wouldn't give me permission for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said to me, what kind of a dog I am?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what will come there, you don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you better stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, little choice that I have, I stayed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I had no-- nothing else to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We stayed-- Was it-- was it unusual to ask requests of the German--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To speak to him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I could talk to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He liked me very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he also always said that if one wants to be clean, you can be clean.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my hair was never cut off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had long braids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like a-- you know, certain camps were for the Red Cross, a showpiece, my hair was the showpiece for Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a young boy in, in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His name was Balsan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the shoeshine boy from SS man Muller-- who was very protective of everybody in, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have had an epidemic of typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He protected everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He-- they-- the-- Muller gave out as a report that they had the flu because otherwise they would have killed us all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This young boy, Muller-- Balsan, went up to Plaszow [NON-ENGLISH] to bring bread for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father by then was in the other camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Every time he went, he tried to give my father a bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
